Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.10,0:00:07.34,Default,,0,0,0,,You know the worst thing about
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.37,0:00:09.08,Default,,0,0,0,,you being the Princess of Friendship?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.24,0:00:10.44,Default,,0,0,0,,The dishes.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.27,0:00:12.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks for taking\Ncare of that, Spike.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.86,0:00:14.53,Default,,0,0,0,,After three events in one week,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.57,0:00:16.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I really needed to\Nrelax with a good book.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.75,0:00:19.33,Default,,0,0,0,,It's kinda funny, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.62,0:00:22.58,Default,,0,0,0,,All these ponies coming to you\Nfor advice about friendship.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.60,0:00:24.35,Default,,0,0,0,,What's funny about that?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.37,0:00:26.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, you know, cause\Nyou used to be famous
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.38,0:00:27.59,Default,,0,0,0,,for being such a bad friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.95,0:00:32.20,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you talking about? I\Nhad good friends in Canterlot.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.30,0:00:35.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, Twilight,\Nlook at the wall.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.31,0:00:38.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you see any photos from\Nbefore we moved to Ponyville?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.04,0:00:40.31,Default,,0,0,0,,And look at you now. The\NPrincess of Friendship.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.70,0:00:45.29,Default,,0,0,0,,This is a disaster!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.41,0:00:47.96,Default,,0,0,0,,All my old friends. I can't\Nremember any of their names
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.98,0:00:50.12,Default,,0,0,0,,right now, but do you\Nreally think that they think
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.14,0:00:51.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm a bad friend?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.42,0:00:54.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I only meant that\Nyou've come so far.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.28,0:00:55.78,Default,,0,0,0,,You're a great friend now and--
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.79,0:00:58.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I feel terrible! I've\Ngot to make it up to them.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.10,0:01:01.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Pack a bag, Spike! We're\Ngoing to Canterlot!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.69,0:01:05.11,Default,,0,0,0,,And make a list of\Nmy friends' names.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.23,0:01:08.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Aw, me and my big mouth.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.64,0:01:17.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Regular subtitles by YayPonies\NWe have muffins!\Nhttp://yayponies.eu/
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.61,0:01:52.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, Twilight.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.62,0:01:54.06,Default,,0,0,0,,You're getting worked\Nup about nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.30,0:01:59.92,Default,,0,0,0,,The only logical place to\Nstart is at the beginning.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.66,0:02:08.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.66,0:02:11.46,Default,,0,0,0,,It's exactly\Nhow we left it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.29,0:02:17.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Look! It's "Predictions\Nand Prophesies!"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.05,0:02:20.29,Default,,0,0,0,,And it's still opened to\Nthe Elements of Harmony!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.86,0:02:25.58,Default,,0,0,0,,And here's that present I\Nwas gonna give Moondancer!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.85,0:02:27.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh, guess she won't be needing that.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.28,0:02:30.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, look! The rest\Nof it's still here!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.09,0:02:35.89,Default,,0,0,0,,How could I have\Nlet this happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.97,0:02:40.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, Twilight.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.74,0:02:42.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Princess Celestia gave\Nyou an assignment.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.02,0:02:44.84,Default,,0,0,0,,No pony could blame\Nyou for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.29,0:02:47.28,Default,,0,0,0,,But look at the way\NI left this place.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.44,0:02:48.78,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a total mess!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.03,0:02:53.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Just like how I\Nleft my friendships.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.34,0:02:56.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I've got to make it up to-
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.26,0:03:01.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, uh, Minuette,\NTwinkleshine, Lemon Hearts,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.72,0:03:03.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Lyra Heartstrings,\Nand Moondancer.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.99,0:03:05.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. Them.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.97,0:03:15.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Spike! Come on!\NWe've got work to do!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.19,0:03:20.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Have you been awake all night?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.69,0:03:22.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I did a little research\Nand I think I know
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.89,0:03:24.23,Default,,0,0,0,,where we can find Minuette.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.62,0:03:25.71,Default,,0,0,0,,That is one of my\Nfriends, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.04,0:03:36.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, it's not too late to\Nforget I opened my big mouth.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.62,0:03:39.35,Default,,0,0,0,,No, Spike. I'm glad you\Nopened your big mouth.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.35,0:03:41.48,Default,,0,0,0,,These ponies have\Nprobably been suffering
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.49,0:03:44.40,Default,,0,0,0,,ever since I left, wondering\Nwhy their supposed friend
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.41,0:03:46.04,Default,,0,0,0,,would treat them so badly.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.07,0:03:50.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Minuette?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.55,0:03:54.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Twilight Sparkle,\Nyou old so-and-so!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.21,0:03:57.40,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing\Nhere? Hey, Spike!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.70,0:03:59.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Look at these wings, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.54,0:04:02.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, grab a picture of me\Nand the Princess, will you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.53,0:04:05.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I tried to tell my coworkers\Nwe used to be friends
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.26,0:04:08.05,Default,,0,0,0,,back when, but they've\Nnever believed me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.17,0:04:16.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait wait wait; really\Nfluff 'em up, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.14,0:04:23.00,Default,,0,0,0,,So what are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.02,0:04:24.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, I know you're\Nhere all the time,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.95,0:04:26.59,Default,,0,0,0,,but you never come to see me!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.03,0:04:29.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! I just had\Nthe greatest idea!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.83,0:04:32.40,Default,,0,0,0,,You want to go see Lemon\NHearts and Twinkleshine?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.69,0:04:35.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course! My old friends!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.17,0:04:39.01,Default,,0,0,0,,It'll be great!\NCome on, let's fly!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.31,0:04:40.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Get it? Heh-heh-heh.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.22,0:04:42.39,Default,,0,0,0,,This is perfect!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.57,0:04:44.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I can apologize to all\Nthree of them at once!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.14,0:04:47.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's hope they're not as\Ntraumatized as Minuette.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.77,0:05:00.79,Default,,0,0,0,,She did! Twinkleshine\Nliterally spit out her oats
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.82,0:05:03.10,Default,,0,0,0,,when she heard you were the\NPrincess of Friendship!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.24,0:05:06.67,Default,,0,0,0,,We saw you at the coronation.\NThat was some shindig!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.17,0:05:07.77,Default,,0,0,0,,You did?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.19,0:05:10.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure! We see you all the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.39,0:05:12.66,Default,,0,0,0,,You remember our old\Nfriend Lyra, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.31,0:05:14.91,Default,,0,0,0,,She lives in Ponyville, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.03,0:05:17.14,Default,,0,0,0,,We're always over\Nthere visiting her
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.16,0:05:18.81,Default,,0,0,0,,or she's coming over here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.91,0:05:21.79,Default,,0,0,0,,We've thought about\Nasking you to join us
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.80,0:05:22.68,Default,,0,0,0,,from time to time,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.69,0:05:25.38,Default,,0,0,0,,but we just sorta\Nfigured you'd moved on.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.49,0:05:27.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.66,0:05:32.19,Default,,0,0,0,,So what brings you by, anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.48,0:05:34.24,Default,,0,0,0,,All those times you've\Ncome back to Canterlot,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.30,0:05:36.33,Default,,0,0,0,,you've never had\Ndonuts with us before.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.66,0:05:38.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, uh, you see...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.14,0:05:42.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I came to apologize.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.01,0:05:45.01,Default,,0,0,0,,For what?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.43,0:05:46.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Before I left Canterlot,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.88,0:05:49.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't really\Nappreciate my friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.97,0:05:51.24,Default,,0,0,0,,And that's because I didn't know
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.26,0:05:53.17,Default,,0,0,0,,how important friendship was.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.35,0:05:56.55,Default,,0,0,0,,But I've learned so much\Nsince I moved to Ponyville.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.97,0:05:59.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I learned what it means\Nto be a good friend
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.68,0:06:02.02,Default,,0,0,0,,and that I certainly wasn't\None to the three of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.53,0:06:07.04,Default,,0,0,0,,So, for all the pain I caused\Nyou, I am truly sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.77,0:06:16.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Aw, come on, Twilight!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.52,0:06:19.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure, it might've stung a\Nlittle bit when you ran off
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.31,0:06:21.50,Default,,0,0,0,,to Ponyville without\Nsaying goodbye,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.67,0:06:24.21,Default,,0,0,0,,but it's not like we weren't\Nused to that from you!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.22,0:06:26.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, we didn't\Ntake it personally.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.93,0:06:28.98,Default,,0,0,0,,But it's really\Ngood to see you now.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.14,0:06:32.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Anypony up for a\Nblast from the past?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.47,0:06:42.33,Default,,0,0,0,,It's our old science lab!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.74,0:06:45.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I have so many great\Nmemories of this place.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.30,0:06:48.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Remember when Lemon\NHearts got her head stuck
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.67,0:06:49.78,Default,,0,0,0,,in that beaker?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.93,0:07:01.17,Default,,0,0,0,,...but according to this book,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.21,0:07:04.06,Default,,0,0,0,,you're supposed to add the\Nsodium chloride first.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.53,0:07:07.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I read ahead and to\Nmake a proper salt lick,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.29,0:07:09.43,Default,,0,0,0,,you need to add\Nthe molasses first.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.43,0:07:12.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I read ahead\Ntoo, Moondancer,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.52,0:07:15.56,Default,,0,0,0,,and I'm sure it said\Nsodium chloride first.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.92,0:07:19.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I've got the wrong\Nbook. That's so hilarious.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.71,0:07:26.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Whatever happened to Moondancer?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.73,0:07:27.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Moondancer?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.21,0:07:30.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, you know,\Nour other friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.76,0:07:35.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh right, Moondancer!\NI remember her!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.30,0:07:37.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder what she's up to.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.12,0:07:39.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I always liked her.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.68,0:07:42.03,Default,,0,0,0,,We just sort of lost\Ntouch after you left.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.31,0:07:45.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I think she went to live out\Nby the stadium, didn't she?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.76,0:07:46.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, let's go see!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.64,0:07:54.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I think this is the place.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.71,0:07:56.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Didn't used to look\Nlike this, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.80,0:08:15.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Moondancer?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.53,0:08:18.89,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you want?\NI'm trying to study.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.37,0:08:21.69,Default,,0,0,0,,It's us! Your old friends--
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.09,0:08:23.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Ugh!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.86,0:08:31.05,Default,,0,0,0,,That's old\NMoondancer, all right!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.08,0:08:32.84,Default,,0,0,0,,She always did like her books.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.19,0:08:36.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, kinda like you\Nused to be, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.46,0:08:38.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Exactly how I used to be.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.82,0:08:57.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, Twilight, we've been\Nwatching her for three days!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.27,0:09:00.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Library, house. Library,\Nhouse. That's it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.87,0:09:02.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Nopony looks at\Nher or says hello
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.99,0:09:04.33,Default,,0,0,0,,or even gives her a smile.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.69,0:09:06.27,Default,,0,0,0,,It's like she\Ndoesn't even exist!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.62,0:09:08.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Was she always like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.19,0:09:09.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, she always\Nwas a little shy.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.90,0:09:11.79,Default,,0,0,0,,But for a while there she\Nwas really starting to
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.80,0:09:12.68,Default,,0,0,0,,come out of her shell.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.02,0:09:14.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Remember when she\Nthrew that party?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.78,0:09:19.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh,right. I think you might\Nhave been busy that day.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.39,0:09:26.08,Default,,0,0,0,,There you are, Twilight!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.44,0:09:28.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Moondancer is having\Na little get-together
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.62,0:09:30.66,Default,,0,0,0,,in the west castle\Ncourtyard. You wanna come?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.26,0:09:35.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Ooh, sorry girls. I got a lot\Nof studying to catch up on.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.97,0:09:45.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Thought she might finally\Nbe letting her guard down
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.91,0:09:47.05,Default,,0,0,0,,a little with that party.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.59,0:09:49.77,Default,,0,0,0,,We invited her out a\Nfew times after that,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.95,0:09:52.22,Default,,0,0,0,,but she was always\Ntoo busy studying.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.61,0:09:55.01,Default,,0,0,0,,So eventually we\Njust stopped asking.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.30,0:09:58.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I had no idea that party\Nwas so important to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.69,0:10:02.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I've got to find a way\Nto make it up to her!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.86,0:10:25.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh my gosh! Moondancer? Is that--?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.06,0:10:25.82,Default,,0,0,0,,SSSSSHHHHH!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.39,0:10:32.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Moondancer? Can I talk\Nto you for a min--
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.76,0:10:33.26,Default,,0,0,0,,SSSSSHHH!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.30,0:10:38.20,Default,,0,0,0,,What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.52,0:10:40.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh, a bubble of silence.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.52,0:10:41.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I haven't seen\Nyou in a while
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.71,0:10:43.52,Default,,0,0,0,,and I thought it might\Nbe nice to catch up.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.04,0:10:44.85,Default,,0,0,0,,For what purpose?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.34,0:10:48.47,Default,,0,0,0,,You know. Cause we're friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.10,0:10:52.07,Default,,0,0,0,,SSSSSHHHHH!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.95,0:11:00.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm really sorry to bother you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.69,0:11:03.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I was just hoping we could go\Noutside and talk for a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.71,0:11:12.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry I skipped your party.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.60,0:11:13.07,Default,,0,0,0,,AAH!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.63,0:11:16.00,Default,,0,0,0,,SSSSSHHHHH!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.49,0:11:20.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Why won't you leave me\Nalone? I'm trying to study!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.98,0:11:23.94,Default,,0,0,0,,You've got the wrong pony.\NI don't have parties.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.10,0:11:25.07,Default,,0,0,0,,You did once.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.31,0:11:27.17,Default,,0,0,0,,And I was so caught\Nup in my own studying
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.18,0:11:29.07,Default,,0,0,0,,that I didn't take your\Nfeelings into account.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.27,0:11:31.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Look, Twilight Twinkle--
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.20,0:11:31.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Sparkle.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.84,0:11:34.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Whatever. I just need to be\Nalone so I can study
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.66,0:11:37.57,Default,,0,0,0,,without some crazy pony trying\Nto make friends, all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.91,0:11:38.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.26,0:11:39.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.11,0:11:42.54,Default,,0,0,0,,How did you get into\Nmy book like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.21,0:11:48.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been studying a\Nnew studying technique.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.35,0:11:50.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I can only do it\Nfor a few minutes,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.19,0:11:52.05,Default,,0,0,0,,but you'd be amazed how\Nmuch you can pick up
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.07,0:11:53.76,Default,,0,0,0,,when you're\Nactually in a book!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.01,0:11:55.56,Default,,0,0,0,,That's one of Haycart's methods.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.57,0:11:56.83,Default,,0,0,0,,You know Haycart?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.94,0:11:58.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course! He's a genius!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.71,0:12:01.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I have a copy of his "Treatise\Non Ponies," you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.10,0:12:07.75,Default,,0,0,0,,What is this place?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.54,0:12:12.75,Default,,0,0,0,,This is where I used to live.\NYou mean I never had you over?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.90,0:12:16.10,Default,,0,0,0,,A first edition of\N"Principles of Magic"!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.90,0:12:18.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey. Didn't I\Ngive this to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.94,0:12:21.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.40,0:12:24.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I did! Look, I even wrote\Nsomething:
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.12,0:12:26.37,Default,,0,0,0,,"To my friend,\NTwilight Sparkle.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.61,0:12:28.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks for introducing\Nme to the classics."
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.18,0:12:31.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I can see by the fact\Nthat you left it here
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.60,0:12:33.15,Default,,0,0,0,,that it meant a lot to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.69,0:12:35.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Look, I didn't\Nbring you over here
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.32,0:12:38.42,Default,,0,0,0,,for even more poignant reminders\Nof what a bad friend I was.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.47,0:12:40.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I brought you here\Nto give you this.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.25,0:12:43.13,Default,,0,0,0,,You can come here\Nwhenever you want
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.27,0:12:45.07,Default,,0,0,0,,and study to your\Nheart's content.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.31,0:12:46.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.71,0:12:49.53,Default,,0,0,0,,But first you've got\Nto do something for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.86,0:12:50.80,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.97,0:12:53.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Have dinner with our\Nold friends tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.89,0:12:56.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't; I'm reorganizing\Nmy biology scrolls.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.81,0:12:59.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been spending a lot of time\Nwith Minuette, Twinkleshine,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.61,0:13:02.50,Default,,0,0,0,,and Lemon Hearts since I've been\Nback. They really miss you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.58,0:13:05.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Look, I already told you,\Nthe last thing I need
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.61,0:13:07.26,Default,,0,0,0,,is a bunch of ridiculous\Nfriend-making
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.27,0:13:08.61,Default,,0,0,0,,keeping me from studying.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.23,0:13:11.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Moondancer, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.72,0:13:13.41,Default,,0,0,0,,A wise pony once taught me
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.44,0:13:15.46,Default,,0,0,0,,that there's more to life\Nthan dusty old books.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.78,0:13:17.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I tried friendship and\Nit's just not for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.26,0:13:19.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Now if you'll excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.80,0:13:25.82,Default,,0,0,0,,What if I taught you\NHaycart's method?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.77,0:13:33.85,Default,,0,0,0,,So, uh, what are you\Nstudying these days?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.98,0:13:36.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Science. Magic. History.\NEconomics. Pottery.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.72,0:13:37.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Things like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.63,0:13:41.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Yowza! You plannin' on being\Na professor or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.46,0:13:42.28,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.90,0:13:45.48,Default,,0,0,0,,So you're just...studying?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.71,0:13:46.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Can I go now?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.65,0:13:48.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Moondancer, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.06,0:13:49.50,Default,,0,0,0,,It's all right, Twilight.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.68,0:13:52.33,Default,,0,0,0,,We're having a good\Ntime. Right, everypony?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.67,0:13:59.25,Default,,0,0,0,,So, uh,Spike, tell\NMoondancer that story about
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.27,0:14:02.12,Default,,0,0,0,,how Twilight had to read a\Nbook about doing a sleepover.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.90,0:14:04.85,Default,,0,0,0,,"Slumber 101"? I've read that.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.08,0:14:09.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, heh-heh, really?\NWell, uh, did you know
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.30,0:14:12.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Lemon Hearts here works\Nat the Canterlot palace?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.43,0:14:15.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, it's true. I do\Nthe big events, mostly.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.07,0:14:18.05,Default,,0,0,0,,State dinners, that\Nsort of thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.53,0:14:23.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Ugh!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.01,0:14:34.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Moondancer! You've got to\Ngive friendship a chance!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.29,0:14:37.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I gave friendship a\Nchance a long time ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.96,0:14:41.21,Default,,0,0,0,,It didn't work out then. It\Nisn't going to work out now.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.86,0:14:44.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Twilight? Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.47,0:14:47.74,Default,,0,0,0,,No. No, I'm not.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.06,0:14:52.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-where are you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.86,0:14:55.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know, Spike, I really\Nmessed this one up.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.13,0:14:57.92,Default,,0,0,0,,That party was\Neverything to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.26,0:15:00.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I can only imagine what\Nit must have felt like
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.33,0:15:01.80,Default,,0,0,0,,when I didn't show up.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.68,0:15:09.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Moondancer! Look\Nat this spread, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.78,0:15:11.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you so much for coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.53,0:15:15.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course! We wouldn't miss one\Nof our best friend's parties!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.74,0:15:17.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Is Twilight coming?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.64,0:15:25.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh. OK.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.44,0:15:29.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, we'll still\Nhave fun, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.25,0:15:32.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.19,0:15:42.81,Default,,0,0,0,,If there was only a\Nway to undo the damage.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.23,0:15:45.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I know what I need to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.02,0:15:48.06,Default,,0,0,0,,And I know just who can help me!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.51,0:16:04.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh. Guess they must have\Ngone back to Ponyville.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.24,0:16:06.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Wheeee!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.83,0:16:11.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa whoa whoa whoa!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.47,0:16:18.10,Default,,0,0,0,,That was AWESOME! We gotta go\Nflying more often, Twilight!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.46,0:16:19.52,Default,,0,0,0,,There you are!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.70,0:16:22.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought you threw in the\Nol' towel and headed home!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.85,0:16:25.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I did head home, but not\Nto throw in the towel.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.63,0:16:29.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I went to get my secret\Nweapon. Minuette, meet--
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.35,0:16:31.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Pinkie Pie!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.33,0:16:32.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi, Minuette!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.81,0:16:36.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Twilight, you didn't say\NMinuette would be here!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.37,0:16:38.54,Default,,0,0,0,,You two know each other?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.59,0:16:41.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, sure! She was one of\NCadance's bridesmaids.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.62,0:16:43.87,Default,,0,0,0,,We hang out all the time\Nwhen she's in Ponyville.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.89,0:16:44.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Didn't you know that?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.03,0:16:48.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Hah! And you call yourself\Nthe Princess of Friendship!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.97,0:16:51.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Twilight briefed me\Non the way here.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.49,0:16:52.64,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll need fifteen\Nbags of confetti
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.67,0:16:54.17,Default,,0,0,0,,and as many hooves\Nas we can get.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.18,0:16:56.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go! We can pass by\Nthe donut place on the way!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.63,0:16:59.04,Default,,0,0,0,,And what are we gonna do?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.23,0:17:00.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Just come with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.77,0:17:13.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Oooh, "A Brief History\Nof the Wagon Harness"!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.00,0:17:19.91,Default,,0,0,0,,"The Life and Times of\NMarwari the Maneless"?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.07,0:17:39.15,Default,,0,0,0,,What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.44,0:17:41.33,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a party. For you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.78,0:17:45.14,Default,,0,0,0,,SURPRISE!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.15,0:17:48.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on in!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.82,0:17:51.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, thanks, but no thanks.\NI don't do parties.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.85,0:17:57.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I know. And I think\Nit's my fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.30,0:17:59.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Back when we were\Nin school together,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.41,0:18:00.97,Default,,0,0,0,,you invited me to a party.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.00,0:18:03.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I was so focused on my\Nstudies that I didn't show up.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.20,0:18:05.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Big deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.77,0:18:07.08,Default,,0,0,0,,It was a big deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.35,0:18:09.98,Default,,0,0,0,,And now that I realize how\Nimportant friendship is,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.02,0:18:12.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd like to make up for my\Nmistake with a new party.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.34,0:18:17.66,Default,,0,0,0,,A party in honor of\Nmy friend, Moondancer!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.55,0:18:21.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, you've got to let\Nme make this up to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.72,0:18:26.46,Default,,0,0,0,,And you think this is\Ngoing to do it, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.62,0:18:28.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Er, Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.51,0:18:30.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, sure, why wouldn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.02,0:18:33.53,Default,,0,0,0,,That was only the first time I\Never put myself out there
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.64,0:18:35.93,Default,,0,0,0,,and then you didn't\Neven bother to show up!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.40,0:18:38.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Then you left town\Nwithout saying goodbye,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.59,0:18:40.63,Default,,0,0,0,,even though we were\Nsupposed to be friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.96,0:18:44.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I was humiliated! I felt\Nlike I wasn't important!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.02,0:18:48.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I never wanted to let myself\Nbe hurt like that again!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.67,0:18:52.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Those three finally convinced\Nme that I had value!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.14,0:18:55.36,Default,,0,0,0,,That other ponies might like\Nme and want to be my friend!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.40,0:18:58.45,Default,,0,0,0,,And YOU! DIDN'T! SHOW! UP!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.68,0:19:14.09,Default,,0,0,0,,You're right; this party can't\Nmake up for the way I hurt you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.33,0:19:17.05,Default,,0,0,0,,But please, don't let my\Nmistake be the reason
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.06,0:19:19.23,Default,,0,0,0,,you can't be friends\Nwith anypony else.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.33,0:19:23.68,Default,,0,0,0,,We were your friends then,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.76,0:19:26.41,Default,,0,0,0,,and we'd be honoured\Nto be your friends now!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.64,0:19:40.99,Default,,0,0,0,,What? That's the librarian,\Nthe book seller, my sister!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.09,0:19:43.84,Default,,0,0,0,,You've got a lot of\Nfriends, Moondancer.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.09,0:19:47.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, Moondancer.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.60,0:19:50.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I've faced magical creatures,\Nthe end of Equestria...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.96,0:19:52.48,Default,,0,0,0,,all sorts of things.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.78,0:19:55.32,Default,,0,0,0,,But seeing how my\Nactions affected you,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.89,0:19:58.47,Default,,0,0,0,,that was one of the worst\Nfeelings I've ever had.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.23,0:20:04.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Twilight.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.93,0:20:07.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I never realized how much\NI needed to hear that.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.19,0:20:22.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Now come on, everypony!\NLet's party!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.75,0:20:23.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.69,0:20:24.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.59,0:20:50.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I think it's time for\Nus to go, Moondancer.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.76,0:20:53.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for helping me\Nmake some new friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.46,0:20:55.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if they are\Nmy old friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.95,0:20:58.57,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll come back and visit soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.79,0:21:00.04,Default,,0,0,0,,That would be great!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.25,0:21:02.95,Default,,0,0,0,,You've still got to teach\Nme that Haycart technique.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.15,0:21:03.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.94,0:21:07.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Um, Moondancer? It\Ngot kinda banged up,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.25,0:21:09.26,Default,,0,0,0,,but here's a little\Nsomething I wanted to give you
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.27,0:21:10.33,Default,,0,0,0,,back at your first party.
